title: Opie & Jim Norton NOV 12 2015 Thu.mp3
description:
Opie & Jim Norton NOV 12 2015 Thu (03:11:55)

On Today's Show:

VIC HENLEY, RON WHITE, BILL BURR, SOPHIE SIMMONS.

Jimmy talks about going to a movie premiere last night, Opie teases that there will be a Presidential candidate on the show later today, they talk about Hillary Clinton possibly wearing a wig, Vic Henley joins them, and they talk about college kids.

(Official) Presidential candidate, Ron White, joins them. He tells them about why he is seriously running for President. Bill Burr joins them. They talk about what Bill is up to and he talks about flying helicopters.

They talk about and watch some videos. They talk about sports stuff.

Gene Simmons' daughter, Sophie Simmons, joins them. They talk about how great she looks now and on her Instagram and she tells them about food problems she's had. They talk about her dad, men vs women,  her music, and they play her new single
